    <title>Windows SysAdmin ProSuite</title>

    <description>
Comprehensive suite of PowerShell and VBScript automation tools for Windows Server
administration and ITSM workstation management.

Includes Active Directory management, SSO integrations, GPO templates,
logging frameworks, incident response utilities, and enterprise-ready
NuGet-distributed tooling.
    </description>

    <summary>
Enterprise-grade Windows SysAdmin and ITSM automation toolkit.
    </summary>

    <tags>
sysadmin itsm powershell vbscript windows-server
active-directory gpo sso automation blueteam forensics nuget
    </tags>

